"{\"uid\": \"jamaicaobserver.com-2024-07-17-jaydon-hibbert-inks-endorsement-deal-kfc-ahead-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Triple jump sensation Jaydon Hibbert, one of Jamaica's most exciting young athletes, has inked a brand partnership with fast food giant KFC.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 140, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 29, \"end\": 36, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toots_Hibbert\", \"score\": 0.9999999647957345, \"rank\": 3.5203846136768073e-08, \"text\": \"Hibbert\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toots_Hibbert\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toots_Hibbert\"}, {\"begin\": 45, \"end\": 52, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9993542068975529, \"rank\": 0.0006451136049773611, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}, {\"begin\": 136, \"end\": 139, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KFC\", \"score\": 0.9999999999988631, \"rank\": 1.2169767032842983e-12, \"text\": \"KFC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KFC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KFC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The partnership with the world under-20 record holder begins on the eve of the 2024 Paris Olympics, where Hibbert will represent Jamaica on the world stage, KFC franchise holder Restaurants of Jamaica (ROJ), said in a press release.\", \"from\": 142, \"to\": 374, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 248, \"end\": 255, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toots_Hibbert\", \"score\": 0.9999999647957345, \"rank\": 3.5203846136768073e-08, \"text\": \"Hibbert\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toots_Hibbert\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toots_Hibbert\"}, {\"begin\": 271, \"end\": 278, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9993542068975529, \"rank\": 0.0006451136049773611, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}, {\"begin\": 299, \"end\": 302, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KFC\", \"score\": 0.9999999999988631, \"rank\": 1.2169767032842983e-12, \"text\": \"KFC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KFC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KFC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"KFC is a long-time supporter of Jamaican sports and athletes.\", \"from\": 376, \"to\": 438, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 377, \"end\": 380, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KFC\", \"score\": 0.9999999999988631, \"rank\": 1.2169767032842983e-12, \"text\": \"KFC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KFC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KFC\"}, {\"begin\": 409, \"end\": 417, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"score\": 0.7407356308133322, \"rank\": 0.3493245656870833, \"text\": \"Jamaican\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We believe in investing in our nation's talented youth, and so we are extremely excited to partner with one of Jamaica's brightest young sporting talents.\", \"from\": 439, \"to\": 593, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 550, \"end\": 557, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9993542068975529, \"rank\": 0.0006451136049773611, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are pleased to welcome Jaydon to the KFC family, and we are delighted to be a part of his journey,\\\" Andrei Roper, ROJ's marketing manager, said.\", \"from\": 594, \"to\": 741, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 634, \"end\": 637, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KFC\", \"score\": 0.9999999999988631, \"rank\": 1.2169767032842983e-12, \"text\": \"KFC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KFC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KFC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Triple jump star Jaydon Hibbert laughs during the signing ceremony for his brand partnership with KFC.\", \"from\": 743, \"to\": 845, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 767, \"end\": 774, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toots_Hibbert\", \"score\": 0.9999999647957345, \"rank\": 3.5203846136768073e-08, \"text\": \"Hibbert\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toots_Hibbert\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toots_Hibbert\"}, {\"begin\": 841, \"end\": 844, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KFC\", \"score\": 0.9999999999988631, \"rank\": 1.2169767032842983e-12, \"text\": \"KFC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KFC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KFC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In addition to being the current world under-20 record holder in the triple jump, Hibbert will now lead Jamaica's medal hopes in the event at the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 847, \"to\": 1008, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 929, \"end\": 936, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toots_Hibbert\", \"score\": 0.9999999647957345, \"rank\": 3.5203846136768073e-08, \"text\": \"Hibbert\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toots_Hibbert\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toots_Hibbert\"}, {\"begin\": 951, \"end\": 958, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9993542068975529, \"rank\": 0.0006451136049773611, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hibbert is also set to represent Jamaica at the World U20 Championships in Lima, Peru later in August.\", \"from\": 1009, \"to\": 1111, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1009, \"end\": 1016, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toots_Hibbert\", \"score\": 0.9999999647957345, \"rank\": 3.5203846136768073e-08, \"text\": \"Hibbert\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toots_Hibbert\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toots_Hibbert\"}, {\"begin\": 1042, \"end\": 1049, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9993542068975529, \"rank\": 0.0006451136049773611, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}, {\"begin\": 1084, \"end\": 1088, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lima_District\", \"score\": 0.9563652292060564, \"rank\": 0.045546980033105276, \"text\": \"Lima\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lima_District\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lima_District\"}, {\"begin\": 1090, \"end\": 1094, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peru\", \"score\": 0.9710243017362805, \"rank\": 0.029834061577734022, \"text\": \"Peru\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peru\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peru\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Roper continued, \\\"Jaydon's attitude and dedication towards track and field has been commendable.\", \"from\": 1113, \"to\": 1209, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He aligns perfectly with everything we hold dear at KFC - leadership, discipline, commitment, dedication, community, nation-building, and all-around Jamaican excellence.\", \"from\": 1210, \"to\": 1379, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1262, \"end\": 1265, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KFC\", \"score\": 0.9999999999988631, \"rank\": 1.2169767032842983e-12, \"text\": \"KFC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KFC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KFC\"}, {\"begin\": 1359, \"end\": 1367, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"score\": 0.7407356308133322, \"rank\": 0.3493245656870833, \"text\": \"Jamaican\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He is a great role model for young athletes.\", \"from\": 1380, \"to\": 1424, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We look forward to what will undoubtedly be a great partnership and are confident he will represent us, both KFC and Jamaica, well at the upcoming 2024 Paris Olympics.\\\"\", \"from\": 1426, \"to\": 1594, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1535, \"end\": 1538, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KFC\", \"score\": 0.9999999999988631, \"rank\": 1.2169767032842983e-12, \"text\": \"KFC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KFC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KFC\"}, {\"begin\": 1543, \"end\": 1550, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9993542068975529, \"rank\": 0.0006451136049773611, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hibbert will appear in upcoming KFC brand and retail marketing campaigns, ROJ said.\", \"from\": 1596, \"to\": 1679, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1596, \"end\": 1603, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toots_Hibbert\", \"score\": 0.9999999647957345, \"rank\": 3.5203846136768073e-08, \"text\": \"Hibbert\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toots_Hibbert\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toots_Hibbert\"}, {\"begin\": 1628, \"end\": 1631, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KFC\", \"score\": 0.9999999999988631, \"rank\": 1.2169767032842983e-12, \"text\": \"KFC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KFC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KFC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, the 19-year-old expressed his enthusiasm over the partnership.\", \"from\": 1681, \"to\": 1754, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am really excited to be partnering with KFC for this Olympic season.\", \"from\": 1756, \"to\": 1827, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1799, \"end\": 1802, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KFC\", \"score\": 0.9999999999988631, \"rank\": 1.2169767032842983e-12, \"text\": \"KFC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KFC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KFC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is an honour to be named the first track and field brand ambassador for KFC.\", \"from\": 1828, \"to\": 1907, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1903, \"end\": 1906, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KFC\", \"score\": 0.9999999999988631, \"rank\": 1.2169767032842983e-12, \"text\": \"KFC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KFC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KFC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Whenever I land in Jamaica, KFC is always my first stop, so this opportunity to represent the brand is truly special to me.\", \"from\": 1908, \"to\": 2031, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1927, \"end\": 1934, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9993542068975529, \"rank\": 0.0006451136049773611, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}, {\"begin\": 1936, \"end\": 1939, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KFC\", \"score\": 0.9999999999988631, \"rank\": 1.2169767032842983e-12, \"text\": \"KFC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KFC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KFC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am excited to see what the future holds.\", \"from\": 2032, \"to\": 2074, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Without question, it's a big deal,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2075, \"to\": 2119, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tags:  HOUSE RULES\", \"from\": 2121, \"to\": 2139, \"entities\": []}]}"